data.description: Huge price reduction!  Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of Annapolis! This charming 4 bed/ 3 bath house offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.    2 separate owners suites with one on each level! Amazing fenced rear yard with plenty of room for a pool.  Step inside to discover an open floor plan that maximizes space and has tons of natural light.  Home has been recently updated and includes beautiful hardwood floors, an upscale kitchen, large open floor plan, and a completely finished lower level!  Continue outside to your own outdoor retreat –large private yard and deck that's perfect for morning coffees, evenings with friends, and anything else you can think of! Home is located on a private cul-de-sac with quick access to Annapolis' vibrant downtown scene, shopping, and dining!  No HOA and easy access to trails and Quiet Waters Park!
